        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-12 font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">Changelog</h1>

        <div class="mt-12">
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">6</span> <span class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">— 21 June 2025</span>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li class="mt-1">Added new payment gateway: Mollie (checkout using a credit card)</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Other minor improvements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">5</span> <span class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">— 20 June 2025</span>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li class="mt-1">Added Telegram notification channel support</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added help resource URLs for notification channels</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed the default Timezone not being applied to Guest users</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed Incidents Acknowledged and Ended timestamps not using preferred timezone</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Other minor improvements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">4</span> <span class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">— 8 June 2025</span>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li class="mt-1">Improved the UI for sidebar and context menu elements</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed an issue preventing public pages from being seen by Guest Users</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed the automatic pause for inactive monitors not working</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Other minor improvements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">3</span> <span class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">— 4 June 2025</span>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li class="mt-1">Added new payment gateway: Paddle (checkout using a credit card)</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added the ability to create free plans on Regular License</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added Domain Name Monitoring functionality (Plan option)</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added Cache Buster option for Monitors (when enabled, every request is unique)</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added the ability to trigger Monitor Incidents when the Request Response contains a specific text</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added the ability to trigger Monitor Incidents when the Request Response does not contain a specific text</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added the ability to define the Request Method for monitors (GET, POST, HEAD, PUT, DELETE, PATCH, OPTIONS)</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added the ability to define the Request Headers for Monitors</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Added the ability to define Request HTTP authentication for Monitors</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Improved the UI for sidebar and context menu elements</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed SSL status being displayed even when SSL monitoring was disabled</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Other minor improvements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">2</span> <span class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">— 12 May 2025</span>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed the Response Time returning zero on some environments</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed Custom Domains for Status Pages not working for the base URL</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed logo and favicon not being saved when creating a new Status Page</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed an issue with the Incidents page not working for non-Admin Users</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Fixed the installation failing on MySQL servers older than version 8</li>
                <li class="mt-1">Other minor improvements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">1</span> <span class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">— 6 May 2025</span>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li class="mt-1">Initial release</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

